# Telegram Signal System — working brief

Finish line confirmed by Joel 2026-07-15 (all recommendations adopted). Canonical spec: [telegram-signal-system](../telegram-signal-system.svx). Research receipts: [.brain/data/telegram-signal-research/](../../data/telegram-signal-research/report-producers.svx).

## Finish line

1. Telegram delivers only the five contract kinds (memories, Joel-owned actions, quality reminders, verified escalations, good-news receipts) — no raw probe noise.
2. Infra signals pass through a bounded XState v5 investigation lifecycle before escalation or digest.
3. Daily and on-demand digests follow the content and voice contract.
4. Actions/reminders have truthful controls tied to real sources (`Done` only with a safe mutation contract).
5. Exact inbound/outbound text queryable from the private ClickHouse journal.
6. `joelclaw messages audit` / `trace` explain any message without ClickHouse archaeology.
7. Contract tests + a measured noise-rate guard under 10% non-actionable.

