- [Narrow ClickHouse access control](clickhouse-access-control.svx)
- [Build the noise-rate guard](noise-rate-guard.svx)

## Operating rules

- Workers build in their owned directories only, never commit; the steering session reviews, integrates, and commits via ShitRat to `main`.
- Every step validates: `bunx tsc --noEmit`, `pnpm biome check packages/ apps/`, focused tests.
- Gateway wiring steps are serialized (one worker at a time touches `packages/gateway`).
- Talon SOS keeps its independent transport until the investigation lifecycle is proven (adopted recommendation).
